name":"SocialSignalUserEdge","node":{"__typename":"User","name":"Emily  Reed","imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1673111152i/425._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg"}},{"__typename":"SocialSignalUserEdge","node":{"__typename":"User","name":"John","imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1167582305i/452._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg"}}]},{"__typename":"SocialSignal","name":"TO_READ","count":827752,"shelfPhrase":"want to read","userPhrase":"827752 people want to read","users":[{"__typename":"SocialSignalUserEdge","node":{"__typename":"User","name":"Eugenia Andino","imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1462708087i/1910._UY200_CR26,0,200,200_.jpg"}},{"__typename":"SocialSignalUserEdge","node":{"__typename":"User","name":"Ryan Dudzinski","imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1687194977i/3100._UX200_CR0,77,200,200_.jpg"}},{"__typename":"SocialSignalUserEdge","node":{"__typename":"User","name":"Rachel","imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1171469514i/4334._UY200_CR10,0,200,200_.jpg"}}]}]},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.ZZ7ZQRF9d_sErL89Admh_w":{"__typename":"Contributor","id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.ZZ7ZQRF9d_sErL89Admh_w","legacyId":5735,"name":"Anthony Burgess","description":"\u003ci\u003eLibrarian Note: There is more than one author in the Goodreads database with this name.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSeriocomic novels of noted British writer and critic \u003cb\u003eAnthony Burgess\u003c/b\u003e, pen name of \u003cb\u003eJohn Burgess Wilson\u003c/b\u003e, include the futuristic classic \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41817486.A_Clockwork_Orange\" title=\"A Clockwork Orange\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eA Clockwork Orange\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e (1962). \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eHe composed also a librettos, poems, plays, screens, and essays and traveled, broadcast, translated, linguist and educationalist. He lived for long periods in southeastern Asia, the United States of America, and Europe along Mediterranean Sea as well as England. His fiction embraces the Malayan trilogy (\u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8823.The_Long_Day_Wanes\" title=\"The Long Day Wanes\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eThe Long Day Wanes\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e) on the dying days of empire in the east. The \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/336190.Enderby\" title=\"Enderby\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eEnderby\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e quartet concerns a poet and his muse. \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16241209.Nothing_like_the_Sun\" title=\"Nothing like the Sun\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eNothing like the Sun\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e re-creates love life of \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/947.William_Shakespeare\" title=\"William Shakespeare\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eWilliam Shakespeare\u003c/a\u003e. He explores the nature of evil with \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/search/search?q=Earthly%20Powers\" title=\"Earthly Powers\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eEarthly Powers\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e, a panoramic saga of the 20th century. He published studies of \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5144.James_Joyce\" title=\"James Joyce\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eJames Joyce\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/31051719.Ernest_Miller_Hemingway\" title=\"Ernest Miller Hemingway\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eErnest Miller Hemingway\u003c/a\u003e, Shakespeare, and \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/17623.David_Herbert_Lawrence\" title=\"David Herbert Lawrence\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eDavid Herbert Lawrence\u003c/a\u003e. He produced the treatises \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2363433.Language_Made_Plain\" title=\"Language Made Plain\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eLanguage Made Plain\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e and \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/112769.A_Mouthful_of_Air\" title=\"A Mouthful of Air\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eA Mouthful of Air\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e. His journalism proliferated in several languages. He translated and adapted \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15638.Cyrano_de_Bergerac\" title=\"Cyrano de Bergerac\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eCyrano de Bergerac\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e, \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1549.Oedipus_the_King\" title=\"Oedipus the King\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eOedipus the King\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e, and \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/61419657.Carmen\" title=\"Carmen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eCarmen\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e for the stage. He scripted \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17568801.Jesus_of_Nazareth\" title=\"Jesus of Nazareth\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eJesus of Nazareth\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e and \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43671008.Moses_the_Lawgiver\" title=\"Moses the Lawgiver\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eMoses the Lawgiver\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e for the screen. He invented the prehistoric language, spoken in \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2005466.Quest_for_Fire\" title=\"Quest for Fire\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eQuest for Fire\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e. He composed the \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/search/search?q=Sinfoni%20Melayu\" title=\"Sinfoni Melayu\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSinfoni Melayu\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e, the \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/168154975.Symphony__No__3__in_C\" title=\"Symphony (No. 3) in C\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSymphony (No. 3) in C\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e, and the opera \u003ci\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/230095.Blooms_of_Dublin\" title=\"Blooms of Dublin\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eBlooms of Dublin\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e. \u003cbr /\u003e","isGrAuthor":false,"works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":362},"profileImageUrl":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1484769559i/5735._UX200_CR0,50,200,200_.jpg","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5735.Anthony_Burgess","viewerIsFollowing":null,"followers":{"__typename":"ContributorFollowersConnection","totalCount":4356},"user":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.lMddr7LF8QEzfaAqkZPAfg":{"__typename":"Book","id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.lMddr7LF8QEzfaAqkZPAfg","legacyId":41817486,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41817486-a-clockwork-orange","viewerShelving":null,"title":"A Clockwork Orange","titleComplete":"A Clockwork Orange","description":"In Anthony Burgess's influential nightmare vision of the future, criminals take over after dark. Teen gang leader Alex narrates in fantastically inventive slang that echoes the violent intensity of youth rebelling against society. Dazzling and transgressive, \u003cem\u003eA Clockwork Orange\u003c/em\u003e is a frightening fable about good and evil and the meaning of human freedom. This edition includes the controversial last chapter not published in the first edition, and Burgess’s introduction, “A Clockwork Orange Resucked.”","description({\"stripped\":true})":"In Anthony Burgess's influential nightmare vision of the future, criminals take over after dark. Teen gang leader Alex narrates in fantastically inventive slang that echoes the violent intensity of youth rebelling against society. Dazzling and transgressive, A Clockwork Orange is a frightening fable about good and evil and the meaning of human freedom. This edition includes the controversial last chapter not published in the first edition, and Burgess’s introduction, “A Clockwork Orange Resucked.”","primaryContributorEdge":{"__typename":"BookContributorEdge","node":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.ZZ7ZQRF9d_sErL89Admh_w"},"role":"Author"},"secondaryContributorEdges":[],"imageUrl":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1549260060i/41817486.jpg","bookSeries":[],"bookGenres":[{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Classics","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/classics"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Science Fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/science-fiction"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Dystopia","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/dystopia"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Horror","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/horror"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Literature","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/literature"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Novels","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/novels"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Banned Books","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/banned-books"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Crime","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/crime"}},{"__typename":"BookGenre","genre":{"__typename":"Genre","name":"Modern Classics","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/genres/modern-classics"}}],"details":{"__typename":"BookDetails","asin":"0393341763","format":"Paperback","numPages":240,"publicationTime":1558422000000,"publisher":"W. W. Norton \u0026 Company","isbn":"0393341763","isbn13":"9780393341768","language":{"__typename":"Language","name":"English"}},"work":{"__ref":"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.Jt780CrmQooAn5DkYMh5nA"},"links":{"__typename":"BookLinks","primaryAffiliateLink":{"__typename":"KindleLink","name":"Amazon","url":"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B005HSGB6W/ref=x_gr_bb_kindle?caller=Goodreads\u0026tag=x_gr_bb_kindle-20","ref":"x_gr_bb_kindle","ebookPrice":"11.99","kuEligible":false,"primeEligible":false},"secondaryAffiliateLinks":[{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Amazon","url":"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0393341763/ref=x_gr_bb_amazon?ie=UTF8\u0026tag=x_gr_bb_amazon-20\u0026linkCode=as2\u0026camp=1789\u0026creative=9325\u0026creativeASIN=0393341763\u0026SubscriptionId=1MGPYB6YW3HWK55XCGG2","ref":"x_gr_bb_amazon"},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Audible","url":"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=A+Clockwork+Orange\u0026i=audible\u0026ref=x_gr_bb_audible\u0026tag=x_gr_bb_audible-20","ref":"x_gr_bb_audible"},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Barnes \u0026 Noble","url":"https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/?ean=9780393341768","ref":null},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"AbeBooks","url":"http://affiliates.abebooks.com/c/64613/77416/2029?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.abebooks.com%2Fservlet%2FSearchResults%3Fisbn%3D0393341763","ref":null},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Kobo","url":"https://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=GwEz7vxblVU\u0026subid=\u0026offerid=361251.1\u0026type=10\u0026tmpid=9309\u0026u1=x_gr_w_bb\u0026RD_PARM1=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kobo.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fsearch%3FQuery%3DA+Clockwork+Orange","ref":null},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Apple Books","url":"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/us/book/isbn9780393341768?at=11lvdC\u0026mt=11\u0026ls=1","ref":null},{"__typename":"BookLink","name":"Google Play","url":"https://play.google.com/store/search?q=9780393341768\u0026